@startuml

class typal {
    +mix(...objects): Object
    +beget(...objects): Object
    +construct(...objects): Function
    +constructor(): Object
}

typal ..> Object : uses
typal ..> Function : constructs
typal ..> RegExp : uses for "before|after"

note right of typal::mix
  Mixes own properties of arguments
  into 'this', supporting before/after layering.
end note

note right of typal::beget
  Sugar for Object.create + mix
end note

note right of typal::construct
  Creates a class-like constructor
end note

@enduml
